c: 7
v: 85
t: "Oo xagga Madyan (waxaan u dirnay) walaalkood Shucayb. Wuxuu yidhi: Dadkaygiyow! Caabuda Allaah, ma lihidin ilaah kale Isaga maahee. Xujo cad xaqiiq waxay idiinka timid xagga Rabbigiin; ee dhammeystira beegga iyo miisaanka oo ha ka dhimina dadka waxyaalahooda, oo ha ku falina fasahaad arlada, inta la hagaajiyey kaddib, sidaas baa idiin khayr badan, haddaad tihiin mu’miniin"